    "cnWords": "也许他离不开。也许他早就被卷进去了。有些人害怕真相被发现，有些人害怕自己的参与被发现。Jimmy是后者。",
    "enAction": "Leans back",
    "enWords": "Maybe he can't leave. Maybe he's already dragged in. Some fear the truth being found, some fear their involvement being found. Jimmy is the latter.",
